changelog.change_log:
- Third map - Mountains;
- New Gear VR remote steering model;
- New plane crash animations;
- Improved plane physics;
- Improved game performance;
- Weapons rebalance.

- Two snow-covered and winter-themed maps: Mountains & Canyons;
- Winter camos for both of our Dogfighter legends: Messerschmitt and Spitfire;
- A winter version of the hangar which introduces the world of Overflight to Holiday Season;
- Enhanced plane physics for better immersion and flight experience.
